formThreeBId.notesToCertificate:
1.It is not possible for us to very phone numbers produced before us by doing individual calling. Thus we have relied on the information provided by the promoters.
2.We have verified information based on the books of accounts and other evidence produced before us. We could able to comment on financial transaction only for other information we have relied on information produced by the promoter of the project. We do not have competence to comment on the carpet area and other measurement mentioned in the certificate. For the same we have relied on the information produce by the management/promoter of the project.
3. Technical data as to measurement and others are taken as provided by the Architect and Engineer to the management.
4. Bank Balance are subject to reconciliation. Issued cheques which are not deposited or under clearing are considered as paid. SimilarlyCheques received and not cleared are taken as received. Balance are verified and taken as per books of accounts. 
5. The project was initially financed by Gruh Finance Limited but the same was merged withBandhan Bank limited. Now, The loan of the Bandhan bank Limited has been Repaid and taken over by  Axis Bank Limited and in Gujrera Portal Details for new Loan taken (Axis Bank Limited) is Pending  to be  Updated and the Promoter has assured that the Updation will be done as early as possible.
6.We have verified copy of the KYC produced before us. In some of the cases KYC  was misplaced from the promoter?s office. Another copy is requested by the promoter, however, to comply the time line we are submitting the same by entering dummy ID as AAAAA0000A  . As without it we cannot submit the return online. The Promoter has assured to produce it as early as possible and before end of the next quarter they will submit the same. 
7. As the Bank Account is changed and no trasaction took place in Axis Bank account as mentioned Deposit and Withdrawal are Zero
8. Following transaction took place in old ICICI RERA account A). Deposit - 35,30,240 B). Withdrawal - 31,80,240, C). Clossing Balance on 30/04/2021 is 3,50,000/-
